metadata.title: Monthly mean sea level Data from Dalian Station of China
metadata.description: The Data include monthly mean sea level Data from Dalian tidal gauge station of China from January 2009 to December 2010. The format is an ASCII(character) format. There is one data file for each month. Code identification, decoding, format check, code transform, standardization, primary quality control, visual inspection, calibration, etc, are carried out before the creation of standard format datasets. The quality control procedure includes range check, illegal code check, station identification check, etc.
metadata.notes:
